# Project Structure

## Core Structure
```
src/
├── types/          # Branded types, primitives
├── core/           # Server, entities, consensus  
├── protocols/      # Wallet, registry
├── storage/        # LevelDB interface & memory impl
├── utils/          # Immutable ops, hashing
└── test/           # TestScenario helpers
```

## Key Files
- [masterplan.md](mdc:masterplan.md) - Complete single-file implementation
- [index.ts](mdc:index.ts) - Main entry point
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Usage examples

## Dependencies
types → utils → protocols → core → storage → infra

## Runtime
- Bun (direct TypeScript execution)
- pnpm for packages
- ESNext modules
